import React from 'react';
import { 
	IonHeader, 
	IonToolbar, 
	IonTitle, 
	IonContent, 
	IonList, 
	IonIcon, 
	IonAlert, 
	IonTabs, 
	IonTabBar, 
	IonTabButton, 
	IonRouterOutlet, 
	IonLabel, 
	IonSpinner, 
	IonFooter, 
	isPlatform, 
	IonItem
} from '@ionic/react';
import { 
	chevronForward, 
	wifiOutline, 
	bluetoothOutline 
} from 'ionicons/icons';

import './index.css';

//import Bluetooth from '../../../components/bluetooth/Bluetooth'
import { BluetoothLE } from '@ionic-native/bluetooth-le';

class Main extends React.Component<{}, {}> {

	componentDidMount() {


	}

	render() {
		return (
			<IonContent class="main-page" scrollY={false}>

				<IonHeader>
					<IonToolbar class="main-toolbar">
						<IonTitle class="main-toolbar-title" size="large">Select A Device</IonTitle>
						<IonIcon icon={chevronForward} class="next-button" slot="end"></IonIcon>
					</IonToolbar>
				</IonHeader>
				<IonSpinner class="single-refresh-spinner"></IonSpinner>
				
				<IonContent class="mid-content">
					<IonList class="device-list">

							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
							<IonItem></IonItem>
				

					</IonList>
				</IonContent>

				<IonFooter>
					<IonToolbar class="footer-toolbar">
						<IonTabs>
							<IonRouterOutlet></IonRouterOutlet>
							<IonTabBar slot="bottom" class="tab-bar">
								<IonTabButton tab="Wifi" href="/scan-devices/wifi" disabled={true}>
									<IonIcon icon={wifiOutline} class="button-wifi"></IonIcon> 
									<IonLabel class="button-wifi button-wifi-label">Wifi</IonLabel>
								</IonTabButton>
								<IonTabButton tab="Bluetooth" href="/scan-devices/bluetooth">
									<IonIcon icon={bluetoothOutline} class="button-bluetooth"></IonIcon>
									<IonLabel class="button-bluetooth button-bluetooth-label">Bluetooth</IonLabel>

								</IonTabButton>
							</IonTabBar>
						</IonTabs>
					</IonToolbar>
				</IonFooter>
			</IonContent>
		);
	};
};
export default Main;
